TITLE: Complete Motion Component Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates a full example of importing and using the Motion component in a React component, including conditional opacity animation based on visibility state.
SOURCE: https://github.com/motiondivision/motion/blob/main/packages/framer-motion/README.md#2025-04-11_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
import { motion } from "motion/react"

export function Component({ isVisible }) {
    return <motion.div animate={{ opacity: isVisible ? 1 : 0 }} />
}
```

